{"_path":"/councilor/service/s4100","_dir":"service","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"公車好重要","description":null,"image":"/images/service/4100-1.jpeg","sequence":4100,"category1":"A. 健全都市發展","category2":"A.4 強化區域交通規劃","link":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1YL6VpHDu3/","author":"陳雅倫","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":"陳雅倫"},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2025-10-20T00:00:00.000Z","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"公車好重要"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"公車好重要"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"倫倫質詢中！繼續向大家報告交通、捷工的質詢，上次強力質詢敦促捷運棕線、捷運銀線，本次多寫一些交通局的部分 ⬇️"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"🚌 老舊公車汰換成低底盤電動公車."},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n5057 公車：目前尖峰時段仍使用小巴，建議改為大車提升載客量。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n5063 公車：公車車體老舊，建議優先汰換為電動公車，方便行動不便長者。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n603、607 公車：中小巴常客滿，導致龜山居民無法上車，建議加開班次。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n大迴龍地區公車班次再增加。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"🚏 新闢與優化公車路線"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nA7 重劃區及產專區人口大增，現有 202 公車搭乘率低，建議新闢公車路線，改善產專區與其他新社區至機捷間的交通銜接。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"🚴‍♀️ YouBike 設點順序不明."},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n部分地區需求高卻未設站，建議交通局訂立明確 SOP，以人流與需求優先。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"🚌 北桃跨市公車協調."},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n新北市公車 946、937 為跨縣市通勤主線，建議桃園交通局與新北市協調，尖峰時段增班以紓解通勤壓力。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"🚓「桃小巴新闢龜山路線」專案施行."},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n龜山因地形關係，像大坑、舊路、新嶺、嶺頂、兔坑、福源、龍壽等過去有免巴行經，後來被裁撤，本席要求龜山過去被減班、裁撤的免費公車，以桃小巴的形式復駛。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"🚗 國道一號林口交流道施工交通黑暗期改善.\n文化一路、復興一路因施工陷入交通黑暗期，每日多起民眾陳情，建議會後召開會勘擬定紓解方案。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s4100-1.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s4100-1.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"公車好重要","depth":2,"text":"公車好重要"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:councilor:service:s4100.md","_source":"content","_file":"councilor/service/s4100.md","_extension":"md"}